contentrichtext.text: {{Wiktionary|Slovak|slovak|Slovakian}} '''Slovak''' or '''Slovakian''' may refer to: * Something from, related to, or belonging to the European country of [[Slovakia]] * [[Slovaks]], an ethnic sub-group of the Western Slavic people * [[Slovak language]], an Indo-European language that belongs to the West Slavic languages * [[Slovak, Arkansas]], United States ==People with the surname Slovak== * [[Hillel Slovak]] (1962 – 1988), Israeli-American musician ==See also== * [[Slovák]], a surname {{disambig}}
